XiaoAI TTS Broadcast Skill

This project contains code adapted from the xiaoai-tts skill in:

  https://github.com/coderzc/open-xiaoai-bridge

The upstream project is licensed under the MIT License. Its copyright notices
are preserved in this package's LICENSE file.

This package adds long-text broadcast support and OpenClaw broadcast-mode
instructions for reading prepared text through a XiaoAI speaker via
Open-XiaoAI Bridge.

This project is unofficial and is not affiliated with Xiaomi, OpenClaw, or the
Open-XiaoAI Bridge maintainers.
